rows.label: qev087706_MSG0002
rows.name: Yes. We've taken out five of the Skells. How about you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087706_MSG0003
rows.name: Impressive. We have also destroyed five.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087706_MSG0004
rows.name: Looks like we have a tie. Nice work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087706_MSG0005
rows.name: Wait. I'm picking up a new signal...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087706_MSG0006
rows.name: Damn them... They have another replica.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087706_MSG0007
rows.name: So there's still one Skell left?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087706_MSG0008
rows.name: Correct. I'll send you the coordinates now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087706_MSG0009
rows.name: Oh? Don't think we can track it on our own?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087706_MSG0010
rows.name: Don't mistake me. I seek only a fair contest.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087706_MSG0011
rows.name: May the gods of war favor the champion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087706_MSG0013
rows.name:
That Buidhe lady sure seems to
have had a change of heart, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087706_MSG0014
rows.name: Perhaps she's finally acknowledged us as friends.[ST:wait ]
